<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.7.4">
<l>kāṉār karikom patocit takaḷiṟē</l>
<l>nāṉā vakainal lavarmaṉ ṉiyanāṅkūr</l>
<l>tēṉār poḻilcūḻ tiruveḷ ḷakkuḷattuḷ</l>
<l>āṉā yaṭiyē ṉukka ruḷpuriyāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Elephant who broke the tusk of the jungle elephant,</l>
<l>Elephant in Tiruveḷḷakkuḷam, encircled by nectar-filled groves</l>
<l>In Nāṅkūr where dwell good people of various kinds,</l>
<l>Grant grace to your servant, me!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
